    <div class="heading-with-actions">

        <div class="signature-row">
          <h1 class="signature" translate="no">drawPolygon(This, Points)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;≡&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">drawPolygon(This, Points, [])</span></h1>


            <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/wx/src/gen/wxDC.erl#L475" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
              <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>

        </div>

      <div class="signature-row">

          <h1 class="signature" translate="no">drawPolygon/3</h1>



          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/wx/src/gen/wxDC.erl#L496" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-spec</span> drawPolygon(This, Points) -> ok when This :: <a href="#t:wxDC/0">wxDC</a>(), Points :: [{X :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>(), Y :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()}].</pre>

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-spec</span> drawPolygon(This, Points, [Option]) -> ok
                     when
                         This :: <a href="#t:wxDC/0">wxDC</a>(),
                         Points :: [{X :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>(), Y :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()}],
                         Option ::
                             {xoffset, <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()} | {yoffset, <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()} | {fillStyle, <a href="wx.html#t:wx_enum/0">wx:wx_enum</a>()}.</pre>

        </div>


<p>Draws a filled polygon using an array of points of size <code class="inline">n</code>, adding the optional offset
coordinate.</p><p>The first and last points are automatically closed.</p><p>The last argument specifies the fill rule: <code class="inline">wxODDEVEN_RULE</code> (the default) or <code class="inline">wxWINDING_RULE</code>.</p><p>The current pen is used for drawing the outline, and the current brush for filling the
shape. Using a transparent brush suppresses filling.</p>
  </section>
</section>
