          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/wx/src/gen/wxDC.erl#L726" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Gets the current layout direction of the device context.</p><p>On platforms where RTL layout is supported, the return value will either be <code class="inline">wxLayout_LeftToRight</code>
or <code class="inline">wxLayout_RightToLeft</code>. If RTL layout is not supported, the return value will be <code class="inline">wxLayout_Default</code>.</p><p>See: <a href="#setLayoutDirection/2"><code class="inline">setLayoutDirection/2</code></a></p>
  </section>
</section>
