          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>If this is a window DC or memory DC, assigns the given palette to the window or bitmap
associated with the DC.</p><p>If the argument is ?wxNullPalette, the current palette is selected out of the device
context, and the original palette restored.</p><p>See: <a href="wxPalette.html"><code class="inline">wxPalette</code></a></p>
  </section>
</section>
