<p>Sets the current pen for the DC.</p><p>If the argument is ?wxNullPen (or another invalid pen; see <a href="wxPen.html#isOk/1"><code class="inline">wxPen:isOk/1</code></a>), the current pen is selected
out of the device context (leaving <a href="wxDC.html"><code class="inline">wxDC</code></a> without any valid pen), allowing the current
pen to be destroyed safely.</p><p>See: <a href="wxMemoryDC.html"><code class="inline">wxMemoryDC</code></a></p>
  </section>
</section>
